    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "Subject: \"FLYING SAUCERS\"",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "[REDACTED] at the U. S. Air Force",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "Base at Mildenhall, England, telephonically contacted writer on",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "February 11, 1953, regarding the new or revived interest in",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "\"flying saucers.\" He stated he did not have any new information",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "to report but did know of an incident that took place several",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "years ago and which the Bureau may desire to check.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "This incident, according to [REDACTED] concerns an article",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "or story on \"flying saucers\" which appeared in a small newspaper",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "with limited circulation, in the Township of Jeffersonville, Delaware",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "Township, Sullivan County, New York. He was unable to recall the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "name of the newspaper but was certain it is the only one published",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "in that area. The story appeared in one of the early 1947 issues or",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "in one of the issues during the last three months of 1946. It was",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "written by a member of the U. S. Armed Forces and of significance is",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "the fact that subsequent issues failed to follow it up by carrying",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "additional stories on \"flying saucers.\" Also significant is the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "fact that it appeared in a small and practically unknown newspaper.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "[REDACTED] states he is merely reporting this for what it",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "text": "may be worth and is being forwarded to the Bureau for any action con-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
